times_](http://argen-times.blogspot.com/2011/02/julio-cortazar-and-
rayuela.html?utm_source=feedburner&utm_medium=feed&utm_campaign=Feed%3A+argen-
times+%28argen-times%29 "http://argen-times.blogspot.com/2011/02/julio-
cortazar-and-
rayuela.html?utm_source=feedburner&utm_medium=feed&utm_campaign=Feed%3A+argen-
times+%28argen-times%29")談及作家的生平。

